            "text": "F.I.S.T.: Forged In Shadow Torch",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " was released on PlayStation and PC in 2021 and now becomes the latest Metroidvania on the Nintendo Switch. The plot follows Rayton, an anthropomorphic rabbit, as he defends the honour of Torch City against a horde of nasty robots known as the Legion. Originality is key when it comes to a crowded genre such as this, and let’s see if ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "F.I.S.T.: Forged In Shadow Torch ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
