        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The cinematics and voiceover work are also absolutely stellar in ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "F.I.S.T.: Forged In Shadow Torch",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". During the cutscenes, it almost felt like watching a Pixar movie. The tales of Rayton and his cohort of other anthropomorphic animals are given depth and meaning by the dark nature of the story, which really comes to the forefront with the dramatic cinematics and punchy, well-delivered dialogue.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "html",
        "html": "<a href=\"https://powera.pxf.io/c/3324894/1258631/15385\" target=\"_top\" id=\"1258631\"><img src=\"//a.impactradius-go.com/display-ad/15385-1258631\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\"/></a><img height=\"0\" width=\"0\" src=\"https://imp.pxf.io/i/3324894/1258631/15385\" style=\"position:absolute;visibility:hidden;\" border=\"0\" />"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "I really enjoyed the story in ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "F.I.S.T.: Forged In Shadow Torch",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " and the way it unravels throughout the game. Rayton used to be an ace pilot in the army and along the way, he encounters a few former members from his squadron (some who are good, but others who are more treacherous). One of Rayton’s early perils involves him trying to rescue his pal Urso (who I ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "think ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "is a bear) and the whole scenario plays out with a ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Final Fantasy VII",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "-esque backdrop, which made me feel like I was chasing down Shinra on the Planet.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
