        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "There’s honestly not a whole lot to grumble about with ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "F.I.S.T.: Forged In Shadow Torch",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". I guess, ultimately, when you look past the cutscenes and the story, it does basically play like a dozen other Metroidvanias and in terms of gameplay, hardly anything original is brought to the table. That said, it does everything adequately; the combat is pretty standard, as is the exploration, and the bosses are solid but not particularly memorable nor challenging.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Lastly, there are nowhere near enough fast travel points, which does make some of the traversal a bit dull, especially when you’re treading over old ground. I kept expecting a new fast travel mechanic to be unlocked as the game world got larger but alas, no. As a result, getting around in Torch City can, at times, be pretty dull!",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 1,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "TL;DR",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
