          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Don’t be put off by all of the cute looking animals on the box art; ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "F.I.S.T.: Forged In Shadow Torch ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "is dark, layered and charming. The story is compelling and whoever did the cinematics deserves a pay rise! Sure, there are some better Metroidvanias out there, but fans of the genre will certainly not feel shortchanged.",
